public class SingleNamedGraphModel
extends com.hp.hpl.jena.rdf.model.impl.ModelCom
implements Model

Model that wraps a single NamedGraph.

"Modelled" after NamedGraphModel but deals with a single NamedGraph rather than a NamedGraphSet.

Author:
Jennifer Cormier, Architecture Technology Corporation

public static NamedGraph verifySingleGraph(NamedGraphSet graphSet)
Utility method that checks that the given named graph set contains exactly 1 graph.

Parameters:
graphSet - NamedGraphSet to check.
Returns:
the single named graph that it contains.
Throws:
RuntimeException - if the set contains no graphs or more than 1 graph.
